Question: One of the images shows a before and after picture of a restyled bookshelf.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/00/a9/8f/00a98fa78664ec99f823485829b58de2.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the image a before picture of a restyled bookshelf?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the image an after picture of a restyled bookshelf?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} xor {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
